# TPC-268 Dataset and Software License

This repository contains both dataset assets and software code. They are licensed under different terms to ensure appropriate use in the academic and open-source communities.

## 1. Dataset License (CC BY-NC 4.0)

All data assets in this repository, including but not limited to the annotation JSON files (e.g., tpc268_annotations.json), taxonomy dictionaries, and any associated image files, are licensed under the **Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License (CC BY-NC 4.0)**. 

This means you are free to share and adapt the dataset for non-commercial academic and research purposes, provided you give appropriate credit to the original authors. 

To view a copy of this license, visit: 
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/

## 2. Software License (MIT)

All software code in this repository, including Python scripts for data splitting, evaluation, and visualization, is licensed under the **MIT License**.

